title: Bands from the 90's influence Shaan's music
text:
Growing up in the Emirates, Shaan rahman grew up listening to western music bands, Backstreet Boys, Westlife , Boney M, ABBA and Michael Jackson.
" I have never been exposed to a lot of western music other than watching some in the two English channels that were available then. I have never learnt music at all than taking up a few keyboard lessons for two weeks," he said.
